# Conventional commit template for ACMI Console
# <type>: <description>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, ci, perf
# Examples:
#   feat: add agent detail timeline
#   fix: resolve Clerk middleware crash on missing key
#   ci: add route QA test runner
#   docs: update deployment instructions
#
# Keep subject under 72 chars. Body wraps at 72 chars.
